extends layout

block content
  if(user)
    h1 Dashboard
    div.container
      form.form-signin(role="form", action="/",method="post",style='max-width:300px;')
            h2.form-signin-heading Edit Profile
            input.form-control(type='text',name='name',value="${user.name}")
            input.form-control(type='text',name='surname',value="${user.surname}")
            input.form-control(type="text",name='username',value="${user.username}")
            input.form-control(type="text",name='age',value="${user.age}")
            input.form-control(type="text",name='degree',value="${user.degree}")
            input.form-control(type="text",name='course',value="${user.course}")
            button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block(type="submit") Update
  if(!user)
    h1 Auth App
  
Create a sign in system when the user can edit his profile and save it and then log out. Assume the user is a student, he should be able to change his name, 
surname ,age, degree and his favourite course